com.tectonica.jonix

Class Onix2Extractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.stream.JonixExtractor
      • com.tectonica.jonix.stream.JonixFilesExtractor
        • com.tectonica.jonix.Onix2Extractor

  • public abstract class Onix2Extractor
extends JonixFilesExtractor
    Simple abstract extractor for ONIX2-only sources. Can be used like that 
     JonixFilesStreamer streamer = new JonixFilesStreamer(new Onix2Extractor()
 {
        @Override
        protected void onProduct(Product product, JonixStreamer streamer)
        {
                // do something with the product..
        }
 });
 
 InputStream is = // your ONIX source
 streamer.read(is);
    Subclasses need to override onProduct(Product, JonixStreamer) and optionally onHeader(Header, JonixStreamer).
